82
00:06:36,212 --> 00:06:40,080
<b>Sadness can be lessened by someone else's sadness.</b>

83
00:06:40,083 --> 00:06:41,780
<b>What are you talking about?</b>

84
00:06:41,785 --> 00:06:44,145
<b>Do you like this?</b>

85
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,925
<b>Myeong Yeo!</b>

86
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:56,225
<b>Hey, tell me what's going on.</b>

87
00:06:56,232 --> 00:06:58,560
<b>Shim Myeong Yeo, explain what's going on.</b>

88
00:06:58,568 --> 00:07:00,730
<b>You saw it. What's there to explain?</b>

89
00:07:00,737 --> 00:07:02,470
<b>Right, but what did I see?</b>

90
00:07:02,472 --> 00:07:04,605
<b>I have glaucoma.</b>

91
00:07:07,410 --> 00:07:10,610
