118
00:08:50,079 --> 00:08:53,875
<b>Oh, it was the landlord's daughter.</b>

119
00:08:54,517 --> 00:08:56,780
<b>They want me to vacate the property immediately...</b>

120
00:08:56,786 --> 00:08:58,980
