126
00:09:19,609 --> 00:09:22,470
<b>use this property for free until now?</b>

127
00:09:22,478 --> 00:09:24,035
<b>Yes.</b>

128
00:09:24,847 --> 00:09:27,075
<b>It was a derelict house.</b>

129
00:09:27,951 --> 00:09:29,645
<b>I'll see you later.</b>

130
00:09:51,474 --> 00:09:53,500
