142
00:10:43,126 --> 00:10:46,955
<b>Hi, Mother. I'm walking up to the second floor now. Yes.</b>

143
00:10:52,235 --> 00:10:54,170
<b>Gosh, Mother.</b>

144
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:57,440
<b>You've gotten so young. Didn't I see you this morning?</b>

145
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:00,065
<b>You should've given me a heads-up about this...</b>

146
00:11:02,578 --> 00:11:05,440
<b>Hello. You're Lee Jang Woo, right?</b>

147
00:11:05,448 --> 00:11:07,915
<b>- Yes. - I'm Jo Young Mi.</b>

148
00:11:08,251 --> 00:11:10,175
<b>Hello.</b>

149
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:12,385
<b>Gosh.</b>

150
00:11:30,606 --> 00:11:35,075
<b>By the way, why were you on the train that day?</b>

151
00:11:36,979 --> 00:11:39,910
<b>Remember that day? I was standing under the maple tree.</b>

152
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:42,775
<b>I thought about it and realized that you were on the train too.</b>

153
00:11:43,419 --> 00:11:45,050
<b>Yes.</b>

154
00:11:45,054 --> 00:11:48,050
<b>As for me, I was running away from home.</b>

155
00:11:48,057 --> 00:11:49,615
<b>What about you?</b>

156
00:11:50,226 --> 00:11:52,160
<b>It was a weekday.</b>

157
00:11:52,161 --> 00:11:55,525
<b>Why did you skip school and get on the train?</b>

158
00:11:59,068 --> 00:12:01,795
<b>The train is approaching...</b>

159
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,965
<b>Hello?</b>

160
00:12:38,674 --> 00:12:40,365
<b>Hello?</b>

161
00:12:41,210 --> 00:12:43,305
<b>Are you...</b>

162
00:12:43,613 --> 00:12:45,405
<b>Jin Ho?</b>

163
00:12:47,016 --> 00:12:48,645
<b>I'm...</b>

164
00:12:49,719 --> 00:12:51,945
<b>your mother.</b>

165
00:12:56,359 --> 00:12:58,360
<b>Kim Jin Ho.</b>

166
00:12:58,361 --> 00:13:00,420
<b>Kim Jin Ho...</b>

167
00:13:00,429 --> 00:13:02,725
<b>is your name.</b>

168
00:13:03,432 --> 00:13:06,465
<b>I gave you that name.</b>

169
00:13:07,103 --> 00:13:10,200
<b>I guess your dad never told you.</b>

170
00:13:10,206 --> 00:13:12,735
<b>My name is Eun Seop.</b>

171
00:13:14,644 --> 00:13:16,435
<b>Lim Eun Seop.</b>

172
00:13:17,146 --> 00:13:19,805
<b>Jin Ho, the thing is...</b>

173
00:13:20,817 --> 00:13:24,845
<b>I'm very ill.</b>

174
00:13:25,788 --> 00:13:27,755
<b>So...</b>

175
00:13:29,892 --> 00:13:33,255
<b>I'd like you to visit me.</b>

176
00:13:34,197 --> 00:13:35,855
<b>You see,</b>

177
00:13:36,732 --> 00:13:38,500
<b>I...</b>

178
00:13:38,501 --> 00:13:41,295
<b>miss you very much.</b>

179
00:13:43,372 --> 00:13:45,835
<b>I'm in Andong.</b>

180
00:13:46,175 --> 00:13:48,935
<b>Can you visit me?</b>

181
00:14:21,444 --> 00:14:24,335
<b>So? Did you meet her?</b>

182
00:14:25,114 --> 00:14:26,540
<b>No.</b>

183
00:14:26,549 --> 00:14:28,715
<b>That day, I didn't go.</b>

184
00:14:28,751 --> 00:14:30,315
<b>Why not?</b>

185
00:14:33,022 --> 00:14:36,815
<b>(Train Ticket, Hyecheon, Andong)</b>

186
00:14:37,593 --> 00:14:39,785
<b>I felt like...</b>

187
00:14:40,696 --> 00:14:44,795
<b>I'd be betraying my parents if I went there to see her.</b>

188
00:14:52,742 --> 00:14:54,365
<b>Also,</b>

189
00:14:55,611 --> 00:14:58,205
<b>I saw you on the platform that day.</b>

190
00:15:08,224 --> 00:15:09,785
<b>What?</b>

191
00:15:09,926 --> 00:15:11,555
