192
00:15:22,171 --> 00:15:24,095
<b>Enjoy.</b>

193
00:15:26,042 --> 00:15:29,275
<b>Shouldn't servers wear masks these days?</b>

194
00:15:29,478 --> 00:15:31,080
<b>Drinking in broad daylight?</b>

195
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:33,745
<b>Yes, I have a reason to drink.</b>

196
00:15:36,152 --> 00:15:40,415
<b>I heard you signed a contract with Shim Myeong Yeo.</b>

197
00:15:41,290 --> 00:15:42,915
<b>Yes.</b>

198
00:15:43,159 --> 00:15:44,290
