199
00:15:44,293 --> 00:15:46,360
<b>Annul it.</b>

200
00:15:46,362 --> 00:15:48,455
<b>I don't like it.</b>

201
00:15:48,731 --> 00:15:50,555
<b>No, I'm good.</b>

202
00:15:53,002 --> 00:15:54,200
