206
00:16:03,279 --> 00:16:06,540
<b>So, annul the contract immediately, Mr. Cha.</b>

207
00:16:06,549 --> 00:16:09,845
<b>If you want to publish my next book, that is.</b>

208
00:16:11,387 --> 00:16:14,655
<b>I have to publish her novel.</b>

209
00:16:15,024 --> 00:16:17,085
<b>There's something I need to find out.</b>

210
00:16:19,295 --> 00:16:24,455
<b>"Mr. Hamil, can people live without love?"</b>

211
00:16:24,867 --> 00:16:26,595
<b>I guess we're done.</b>

212
00:16:27,770 --> 00:16:31,135
<b>Is there anything you want?</b>

213
00:16:32,308 --> 00:16:33,370
