214
00:16:33,376 --> 00:16:37,605
<b>I really need you as a writer.</b>

215
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:39,780
<b>Tell me.</b>

216
00:16:39,782 --> 00:16:43,675
<b>What can I do to publish your next book?</b>

217
00:16:47,723 --> 00:16:50,350
<b>"Instead of answering my question,"</b>

218
00:16:50,359 --> 00:16:54,125
<b>"he took a sip of mint tea, which is good for one's health."</b>

219
00:17:04,073 --> 00:17:05,765
<b>We're here.</b>

220
00:17:09,211 --> 00:17:11,645
<b>I know you're not sleeping.</b>

221
00:17:11,947 --> 00:17:15,045
<b>"He looked at me without saying a word."</b>

222
00:17:16,552 --> 00:17:18,215
<b>Get out.</b>

223
00:17:22,958 --> 00:17:24,290
<b>I don't want to.</b>

224
00:17:24,293 --> 00:17:26,390
<b>"He probably thinks I'm still too young..."</b>

225
00:17:26,395 --> 00:17:30,730
<b>"and there are many things in the world I'd better not know."</b>

226
00:17:30,733 --> 00:17:32,000
<b>Hurry up and do it.</b>

227
00:17:32,001 --> 00:17:33,565
<b>What?</b>

228
00:17:33,636 --> 00:17:35,565
<b>Okay.</b>

229
00:17:42,311 --> 00:17:45,375
<b>- I'm leaving. - No, wait.</b>

230
00:17:45,915 --> 00:17:47,545
<b>I'll do it.</b>

231
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:01,555
<b>"Mr. Hamil, why aren't you answering me?"</b>

232
00:18:32,094 --> 00:18:36,325
<b>"Mr. Hamil, can people live without love?"</b>

233
00:18:43,372 --> 00:18:45,365
<b>Is this...</b>

234
00:18:45,574 --> 00:18:47,505
